@NODE HiSTORY "THE HiSTORY OF 'CALLER-SPY' BY SPiDeR/OSiRiS"


                         THE HiSTORY OF 'CALLER-SPY'
                ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


VERSiON 0.1 : FiRST iNTERNAL RELEASE, MADE AS `CLI-ONLY`-TOOL

VERSiON 0.2 : iNTERNAL RELEASE, A FEW BUGS FiXED

VERSiON 0.3 : BETA-RELEASE

VERSiON 0.4 : iNTERNAL RELEASE, SOME BUGS REMOVED

VERSiON 0.5 : BETA RELEASE, SOME BUGS FiXED

VERSiON 0.6 : BETA RELEASE, SEEMS TO RUN STABLE

VERSiON 0.7 : TOTALLY REWRITTEN TO A DOOR-UTIL, SOME MINOR BUGS KILLED

VERSiON 0.8 : ADDED USER-CONFIGURATION-SCREEN, ADDED MULTi-NODE-COMPATiBiLiTY,
              SPEEDED THE WHOLE THING UP (UP TO TWO TIMES FASTER!!)

VERSiON 0.9 : DESIGNED THE STYLE TOTALLY NEW
              ADDED ASCII,AMIGA-ANSI,IBM-ANSI - SELECTION
              ADDED COLOR-CONFIGURATION-SCREEN  (Cool, eh?)
              NOW THE FRONT-ANSI CAN HAVE AN UNLIMITED NUMBER OF LINES

VERSiON 1.0 : FIRST PUBLiC VERSiON
              NOW LOCAL-UPLOADS ARE COUNTED, TOO
